  array('id_index'=>9184,'id'=>241679,'name'=>'Vosges','description'=>'Do you know chocolate? Vosges Chocolate knows it very well. The owner of Vosges Haut Chocolate is Katrina Markoff, who trained in confectionary at Le Cordon Bleu in Paris, and then worked in three European countries as well as in Southeast Asia and Australia before heading to Chicago and founding Vosges. 

